members.name: detail
members.description: Specifies some detail information about the Event, depending on the type of the event. For this event type, indicates the repeat number for the animation.

members.name: view
members.description: The view attribute identifies the AbstractView [DOM2VIEWS] from which the event was generated.

members.name: initTimeEvent
members.description: The initTimeEvent method is used to initialize the value of a TimeEvent created through the DocumentEvent interface. This method may only be called before the TimeEvent has been dispatched via the dispatchEvent method, though it may be called multiple times during that phase if necessary.
